      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "### Changed\r\n- Discontinued support for **behkhaan**. This site relies on **SPA-based routing**, which prevents reliable data extraction from user-provided URLs. Supporting it would require a more complex approach, so it has been suspended for now.\r\n- Removed HTML-based selectors from **taaghche** and **goodreads** in favor of structured data extraction.\r\n- Extracted `publisher` and `datePublished` from **`__NEXT_DATA__`** on **goodreads**.\r\n\r\n### Added\r\n- Added support for new variables: `language` and `url`.\r\n- Added missing support for the `translator` variable on **amazon**.",
